I am glad for the guys who came out to realize the numerical advantage in the match with Dynamo Minsk
Bob Hartley: I am glad for the guys who came out to realize the numerical advantage in the match with Dynamo Minsk
Avangard head coach Bob Hartley summed up the results of the KHL regular-season match against Dynamo Minsk (2: 1).
